{"tid":718275,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【港視匯豐聯手】HKTVmall網購可用PayMe找數","createTime":"2018-06-26T16:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T03:02:50.000Z","uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"75f09fff82adcc313c280cebf3977f75bd64092c","tid":718275,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/pic/0/10/16/18/10161811_953767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Fpic%2F0%2F10%2F16%2F18%2F10161811_953767.jpg&h=1952b517&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n匯豐手機支付應用程式PayMe，繼去年2月推P2P(個人對個人)轉帳服務後，昨宣佈與香港電視(01137)旗下HKTVmall合作，推出其首個P2M(個人對商戶)支付服務，讓PayMe用戶於今周稍後日子可在HKTVmall網購作支付之用。<br />\n<br />\n其客戶在HKTVmall透過PayMe付款，屆時只需幾個簡單步驟，在HKTVmall應用程式上點擊結帳，頁面將自動轉往PayMe應用程式進行付款。確認付款成功後，系統會即時處理定單。<br />\n<br />\n香港電視主席王維基表示，客戶用PayMe在HKTVmall網購僅需2秒便可完成交易，較用信用卡網購需時更快。因應是次與PayMe合作，亦有短期推廣優惠，包括消費滿400元，可即時獲贈50元折扣優惠、購買指定電器及電子產品可享首件95折及第2件92折，以及抽獎，優惠將於7月陸續完結。他指，去年在HKTVmall購物的客戶人數達47.7萬，料今年上半年的購物人數將可打破去年的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n就日後會否與支付寶、微信支付等支付機構合作，王維基表示，一直致力尋找方便客戶支付的方式，故不排除與其他機構合作，並說︰「做生意好實際，我們會與最大、最多人使用、受港人歡迎及信任的機構合作」。<br />\n<br />\n匯豐環球商戶解決方案主管Brain McKenney表示，自推出PayMe後，登記用戶及交易量顯著增長，現服務進入另一個新階段，與HKTVmall合推P2M支付服務，期望未來與更多的商戶合作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.orangenews.hk/finance/system/2018/06/26/010092811.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.orangenews.hk%2Ffinance%2Fsystem%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F010092811.shtml&d=R0syECZasz%2BGAEeQHIG%2BTpUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=4eee0960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.orangenews.hk/finance/system/2018/06/26/010092811.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e183ae18da32c923e4b7ea2f0286b98ca569d7e5","tid":718275,"uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:06:24.000Z","msg":"<code>做生意好實際，我們會與最大、最多人使用、受港人歡迎及信任的機構合作</code><br />\n<br />\n暗寸緊邊間？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97dfd45234b824bcba924600c4a0a723d4c8746","tid":718275,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:08:02.000Z","msg":"PayMe越搞越大 最好推埋英國同印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9292a9266ec2025367edd829cc01e11219ae8b0d","tid":718275,"uid":132587,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:12:21.000Z","msg":"搞好d送貨先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c363a6e51086557436f7a31a55aaf790d8769fc","tid":718275,"uid":38891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:13:14.000Z","msg":"八達通呢？"},{"pid":"705086b85a4e19ce964c76432bf5d4cad141ff1b","tid":718275,"uid":58249,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:15:47.000Z","msg":"搞掂個身份證upload先啦含家剷"},{"pid":"9b59b97fc810236a9ce3361d4638fc880ca6bb8a","tid":718275,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"他指，去年在HKTVmall購物的客戶人數達47.7萬，料今年上半年的購物人數將可打破去年的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n連燈仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d37204534a52386caf7e91036e43871b36c7311d","tid":718275,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}